     F* GET QR
     FAM#PL08 IF  E           K        DISK
     F* GET SHORTAGE
     FALDPP65 IF  E           K        DISK
      *---------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 AUHN
     I                                        1   5 A6MHN1
     I                                        6  10 A6MHN2
     I                                       11  12 AUHN3
      *---------------------------------------------------
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K1NONY  40
     C                     KFLD           K1DOCK  2
     C                     KFLD           A6ORNO 12
      *---------------------------------------------------
     C                     MOVE A6NONY    K1NONY
     C                     MOVELA6NUKE    K1DOCK
     C                     MOVELA6MHN3    AUHN3
      *---------------------------------------------------
     C           KEY1      SETLLAM#PL08
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY1      READEAM#PL08                  30
     C   30                LEAVE
      *
     C                     MOVE R1SHID    WWDATE  80
     C           AUHN      IFEQ R12HN
     C           WWDATE    ANDGE20210701
      *
     C                     MOVELR12D      A6UKAN
      *---------------------------
     C           A6UKAN    CHAINALDPP65              31
     C           *IN31     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     Z-ADDAFODAT    A6ODAT
     C                     Z-ADDAFOTIM    A6OTIM
     C                     Z-ADDAFRDAT    A6RDAT
